              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "CHSEP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Radiochemical separation of the fission",
                " products from Th-232(n,f) and U-235(n,f). The",
                " quantity",
                "         R=Ast(Th)*A2/(Ast(U)*A4) is measured, were",
                "         Ast(Th)= activity of product in Th-232(n,f),",
                "         A2= activity of Mo-99 in U-235(n,f),",
                "         Ast(U)= activity of product  in U-235(n,f),",
                "          compilation by Rider(NEDO 12154-3B) was used.",
                "         A4= activity of Mo-99 in Th-232(n,f).",
                "The yields in thorium fission were then determined",
                "according to Yi(Th) = R*Yi(U)*Yst(Th)/Yst(U)"
              ]
            },
